Only the very first line of every file in this directory is considered by
evdaemon.

key - Bit values of keys evdaemon should monitor. Defined using the same syntax
      as keys displayed in /proc/bus/input/devices, i.e. at most 16 hex values
      per block, at most 12 blocks, most significant bit first.
rel - Bit values of relative axis evdaemon should monitor. Defined
      using the same syntax as relative axis displayed in
      /proc/bus/input/devices, i.e. at most 16 hex values per block, at most
      12 blocks, most significant bit first.
